{"tid":1250501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬持疑似警棍叫示威者走","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T20:56:22.000Z","uid":6181,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"33197f93d01968245b7ce629117cb9c87a40bb1e","tid":1250501,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"【02:40更新】【被困警員離開警總】<br />\n【口罩男持疑似警棍叫示威者走】<br />\n<br />\n多間大專院校的學生會，不滿政府沒回應，撤回《逃犯條例》修訂等訴求，發起堵塞夏慤道，及包圍警察總部，警總出入口被阻塞，入面的人無法進出。<br />\n<br />\n直到凌晨兩時四十分，其中一個側門清走障礙物，警員陸續離開警總。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #警總 #示威者 #警察總部<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/198559761061678?s=100003716520476&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F198559761061678%3Fs%3D100003716520476%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=858fdcd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/198559761061678?s=100003716520476&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n補返link<br />\n<br />\n3:06開始 班狗拎警棍出黎趕人"},{"pid":"f7bc2dac7021726222e0910c92686e9be57cd5da","tid":1250501,"uid":6181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:55:38.000Z","msg":"點解可以完全冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff00d8a12cc238b79a212e9a05c799fd0b17d2b","tid":1250501,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2a00ac3dc24e38c2734951e48f68cbb9b22dba6c","tid":1250501,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea40e628cd27f17d28e47ad64170662c7acd8a42","tid":1250501,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d5850f96f9d142f7e5f6d5